## ğŸš€ Deployment

### Docker Deployment
```bash
# Build and run with Docker
docker build -t weather-mlops .
docker run -p 8000:8000 weather-mlops
```

### Production Deployment
```bash
# Start production server
uvicorn src.deploy.app:app --host 0.0.0.0 --port 8000 --workers 4
```

